	gs.log("auto cancel 1st log");
	// Add your code here
var ritm = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
ritm.addQuery('sys_id', current.document_id);
ritm.query();
if (ritm.next()) {
		gs.log("auto cancel 2nd log");
    ritm.state = 4;
//    ritm.stage = 'waiting_for_approval';
    ritm.update();
}

var req = new GlideRecord('sc_request');
req.addQuery('sys_id', current.document_id);
req.query();
if (req.next()) {
		gs.log("auto cancel 3rd log");
    req.approval = 'requested';
    req.request_state = 'closed_cancelled';
    req.update();
}
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>sydney.e</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-11-16 06:14:45</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>711c0c442f1395107fcffe7cf699b6f2</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_name>auto cancel</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_711c0c442f1395107fcffe7cf699b6f2</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>sydney.e</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-11-22 05:53:41</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=711c0c442f1395107fcffe7cf699b6f2"/></record_update>
